RoadWeaver Credits and Notices

This project includes code adapted from:

- settlement-roads-new (CC0 1.0 Universal)
  Author: Countered
  Source: https://github.com/countered/settlement-roads-new
  Notes: Portions of the road generation and decoration system were ported, including but not limited to:
  - Feature configuration and placement data formats (configured/placed features)
  - Road generation logic (A* pathfinding, segment interpolation, surface placement)
  - Decoration system (lampposts, fence waypoints, distance signs, buoys)
  - Biome-aware wood selection

The original work is dedicated to the public domain under CC0 1.0; attribution is not legally required, but is provided here out of respect and for transparency.

